race.description: Albury Demolitions Country Boosted Class 1 Hcp
race.comment: DOUBTFREE (4) is a locally trained gelding who capped off some strong form when securing a well-deserved maiden in at Cootamundra 6 days ago. It is a good sign to see him backing up so quickly, and he can repeat the dose. AUTUMN BREAK (5) clung on to a gritty win when making his debut in a strong maiden field at Wagga just over 6 weeks ago. He is a very promising type who will relish the extra furlong on offer here. Go again. DEEBAA (3) ruined her chances last start by hanging the whole way. She did everything right in a recent trial, so she is worth another chance. Each-way. SONIC SCENE (1) built nicely to an impressive maiden win at Wagga 12 days ago, scoring by more than 3 lengths. He meets a tidy field here but can measure up again. ROULLOTTIE (6) followed up her overdue maiden win with a sound fourth at Wagga last time out. She has the pole position and is worth including in all combinations.
